<p style="text-align: center;font-size: 120%;"><b>Update Year 1 (2007, 2008): Contract and Expenditure Update</b></p>


<p>The California Air Resources Board (ARB) had allocated over $44 million of Proposition 1B funds to the San Joaquin Valley Air Pollution Control District (SJVAPCD) for heavy-duty truck replacement and retrofit projects for Year 1 of the Program. Applications were accepted during late summer 2008. All of the funds for Year 1 have been contracted.</p>

