<a name="WoodStoveChangeOut"> </a>
<h1 class="button-text-wht">Burn Cleaner Program </h1>
<p>The Burn Cleaner Program is offered to help Valley residents upgrade their current wood-burning devices and open fireplaces to natural or propane gas devices, or clean pellet devices to alleviate the problem of particulates, which are a significant problem during the fall and winter months.</p>
  
 <div id="wrapper" style="width:100%; margin: 20px auto; text-align:center">
<div style="padding: 10px; text-align:center; width: 444px; border:2px solid #FF0000; color: #FF0000; position:relative; left:auto; right:auto; height:43px">
	<b><span class="noapp" style="vertical-align: middle">
	<a target="_blank" href="BurnCleaner/2013/WEBSITERETAILERCONTACTLIST32613.pdf">Burn Cleaner Program Contracted Retailers</a> </span> </b></div>
</div>

<ul> 
<!--<li><a href="BurnCleaner/Burn_Cleaner_Guidelines.pdf">Burn Cleaner Program Eligibility Criteria and Application Guidelines (Fillable PDF)</a></li> -->
<!--<li><a href="BurnCleaner/Burn_Cleaner_Payment_Procedures_Packet-Fillable.pdf">Burn Cleaner Claim for Payment Procedures Packet (Fillable PDF)</a></li> -->
<li>
<a target="_blank" href="BurnCleaner/2013/Burn-Cleaner-Guidelines-2010-Revised-5-1-13.pdf">Burn Cleaner Program Eligibility Criteria and Application Guidelines</a></li>
<li>
<a target="_blank" href="BurnCleaner/2013/2_Burn_Cleaner_Application_LE_W9-fillable-extended.pdf">Burn Cleaner Program Application</a></li> 
<li><a target="_blank" href="BurnCleaner/2012/2012BurnCleanerflyer.pdf">Burn Cleaner Program 
Flyer</a> </li>
<li>
<a target="_blank" href="BurnCleaner/2010/Claim%20for%20Payment%20-%20Burn%20Cleaner%20Program%20interactive.pdf">
Claim for Payment</a></li>

</ul>
<p>For current updates regarding the Burn Cleaner Program, please sign-up on the <a target="_blank" href="http://lists.valleyair.org/mailman/listinfo/burn_cleaner_program">SJVAPCD's list serve</a>. </p>


