<!--<p>The District is pleased to announce that additional funding is available for the CGYM Program. The District will begin accepting applications for the program on Monday, April 11, 2011 at 7:30 am. There are a limited number of vouchers available for each of the District’s eight (8) counties, and vouchers will be distributed on a first-come, first-served basis until funding is exhausted.
</p>

<p>To submit an application for a CGYM voucher, please call or visit one of the District’s three (3) regional offices during normal business hours.
</p>
<p >
<ol style="padding-left: 130px;">
<li>Northern Region Office, Modesto:  (209)557-6485</li>

<li>Central Region Office, Fresno:    (559)230-6185</li>

<li>Southern Region Office, Bakersfield: (661)392-5685</li>
</ol>

