<p>Office Hours: Monday – Thursday 7:30 am to 5:30 pm and Friday 8:00 am to 5:00 pm, closed alternating Fridays
</p>
<p>
A list of participating recyclers, including addresses and hours of operation, will be provided on the back of each executed CGYM voucher distributed by the District.  There are a total of nine (9) approved recyclers in the program with at least one participating recycler in each of the eight (8) counties of the District.  As a reminder, you must have an executed voucher from the District prior to recycling your existing lawnmower.      
</p>-->

<!--<table>
