<a name="CordlessLawnMachine"> </a>
<h1 class="button-text-wht">Cordless Zero-Emission Commercial Lawn & Garden Equipment Demonstration Program</h1>

<p>The San Joaquin Valley Air Pollution Control District (District) is currently working with participating commercial lawn care end-users to demonstrate the performance and durability of cordless zero-emission commercial lawn and garden equipment.  The Cordless Zero-Emission Commercial Lawn & Garden Equipment Demonstration Program (Demonstration Program) provides opportunities to utilize new, zero-emission equipment to promote air-friendly operations and to develop greener business practices.  Currently, available zero-emission equipment is limited in the commercial sector and the demonstration would allow participants to gain hands-on familiarity with the equipment.  The data obtained through in-use testing and reporting would help further improve, and encourage the use of clean technologies.  The Demonstration Program is scheduled to end in May 2013. </p>

<div id="wrapper" style="width:100%; margin: 20px auto; text-align:center">
	<div style="padding: 10px; text-align:center; width: 444px; border:2px solid #FF0000; color: #FF0000; position:relative; left:auto; right:auto; height:43px">
					<b><span class="noapp" style="vertical-align: middle">
				Application Period is Closed</span> </b>
	</div>
</div>
<p>Equipment User Survey Documents:</p>


<ul>
<li>
<a href="CordlessLawnMachine/SurveyInstructionFormFINAL.pdf">Equipment User Survey Instructions</a></li>
<li>
<a href="CordlessLawnMachine/Commercial_LG_participant_surveyFINAL_fillable-ExtFeatures.pdf">Equipment User Survey Form 
</a></li>
</ul>





